{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"LDC4","author":"Weedust"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"3fe1bb5a-4222-5cb2-84c1-6af330254514","excerpt":"\n因为工作调动的原因，现在技术栈切到了 Vue + Express  \nVue上手倒是挺快，但是看完一遍文档还是花费了一周  \n然后工作两周，发现很多东西都记不住，印象逐渐消失  \n\n","html":"<p>因为工作调动的原因，现在技术栈切到了 Vue + Express<br>\nVue上手倒是挺快，但是看完一遍文档还是花费了一周<br>\n然后工作两周，发现很多东西都记不住，印象逐渐消失  </p>\n<!-- more -->\n<h2>官方文档</h2>\n<h3>教程</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Vue</strong>：<a href=\"https://cn.vuejs.org/v2/guide/\">https://cn.vuejs.org/v2/guide/</a></li>\n<li><strong>Vue Cli</strong>: <a href=\"https://cli.vuejs.org/zh/guide/\">https://cli.vuejs.org/zh/guide/</a></li>\n<li><strong>Vue Router</strong>: <a href=\"https://router.vuejs.org/zh/guide/\">https://router.vuejs.org/zh/guide/</a></li>\n<li><strong>Vuex</strong>: <a href=\"https://vuex.vuejs.org/zh/guide/\">https://vuex.vuejs.org/zh/guide/</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>API</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Vue: <a href=\"https://cn.vuejs.org/v2/api/\">https://cn.vuejs.org/v2/api/</a></li>\n<li>Vue Router: <a href=\"https://router.vuejs.org/zh/api/\">https://router.vuejs.org/zh/api/</a></li>\n<li>Vuex: <a href=\"https://vuex.vuejs.org/zh/api/\">https://vuex.vuejs.org/zh/api/</a></li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<p>虽然Vue3.0快出来，但是要普及估计还得要一段时间。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2>基础</h2>\n<h3>Vue实例</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> vm <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Vue</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    el<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'#example'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 模板中的ID</span>\n    data<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>       <span class=\"token comment\">// 数据</span>\n        <span class=\"token comment\">// 状态值，响应式的数据</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    methods<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>    <span class=\"token comment\">// 方法</span>\n        <span class=\"token comment\">// 一般为处理状态的方法</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Object.freeze()</code> 可以阻止响应式</p>\n<p>带有$前缀的是vue内置属性</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Vue学习与实践","date":"2019-09-25 09:44:27","tags":null,"category":"学习","draft":true}},"allNavigationJson":{"edges":[{"node":{"name":"分类","link":"/cats"}},{"node":{"name":"标签","link":"/tags"}}]},"allGitalkJson":{"edges":[{"node":{"clientID":"49e26d4dd7cf72ebb64d","clientSecret":"e593383921b7f8ef0b08db7fc8c109828a8e50d1","repo":"blog","owner":"ldc4","admin":["ldc4"]}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/vue/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/plan/2019-down/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"2019年下半年学习计划","tags":null,"category":"计划","draft":null}},"next":null}}